sequenceDiagram
  participant FE as Frontend
  participant BE as Backend
  participant OW as Optimizer workers

  FE->>BE: REST request (update config / solve / cancel)
  Note over BE: Create task + persist run state
  OW->>BE: Long-poll endpoint
  BE-->>OW: Task payload / cancel signal
  Note over OW: CP-SAT phases (long-running)
  loop While CP-SAT runs
    OW->>BE: WebSocket logs/progress
    BE-->>FE: Intermediate status
  end
  OW->>BE: Return schedule artifacts
  Note over BE: Aggregate status + store outputs
  BE-->>FE: Final result payload
  Note over FE: Inspect result + continue editing
